                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.51/675.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-09-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 5, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President is to issue a proclamation convoking Congress in extraordinary
                    session relative to granting power for issuance of bonds, reducing the budget
                    and enacting a moratorium law.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jefferson</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
